text.name: Text 5
text.value:
Hi! I’m Jess Shulman—a photographer, designer, and lover of all things creative. 
  
I get my inspiration every day from the lovely humans around me, this amazing earth, and all the little things that make life beautiful. 

You can find me gardening, behind the camera, sketching, making something handmade, spending time with my favorite people — whatever it is, you can expect I’ll be laughing :)

text.name: Text 8
text.value:
I care deeply about the earth, sustainability, and am always looking for ways to bring the beauty of nature into your daily life, whether it’s flowers from the farm or inspirations in my designs. 

I'd love to help you create something meaningful that captures your story, elevates your brand, and brings out the art in what you do.

I can’t wait to meet you and help bring your ideas to life — send me a message and let’s make something beautiful together!

text.name: Text 10
text.value: From lifestyle portraits to event coverage, I deliver polished, professional images tailored to your needs. My approach emphasizes natural light, authentic emotion, and thoughtful composition to ensure every image stands out.

text.name: Text 12
text.value: I also specialize in creating custom designs, from branding and logos to marketing content and product design. With every project, I blend creativity, vibrant color palettes, and aesthetic patterns to make imaginative designs that align beautifully with your vision.
